column2: SELECT DISTINCT  	po.objid AS phot_id, po.ra AS phot_ra, po.dec AS phot_dec,  	ISNULL(pz.z, #) AS phot_z, ISNULL(pz.zerr, #) AS phot_zerr,  	po.type AS phot_type, po.ndetect AS phot_ndet, po.clean AS phot_clean,  	ISNULL(sp.specobjid, #) AS spec_id, ISNULL(sp.ra, #) AS spec_ra, ISNULL(sp.dec, #) AS spec_dec, 	ISNULL(sp.z, #) AS spec_z, ISNULL(sp.zerr, #) AS spec_zerr,  	ISNULL(sp.class, #) AS spec_class, ISNULL(sp.instrument, #) AS spec_inst,  	ISNULL(sp.zwarning, #) AS spec_zwarning,    	ISNULL(sp.snmedian, #) AS spec_snmedian,    	ISNULL(pl.platequality, #) AS spec_platequality,  	po.modelmag_u AS modmag_u, po.modelmagerr_u AS moderr_u, po.fibermag_u AS fib3mag_u, po.fiber2mag_u AS fib2mag_u, po.extinction_u AS extinct_u,  	po.modelmag_g AS modmag_g, po.modelmagerr_g AS moderr_g, po.fibermag_g AS fib3mag_g, po.fiber2mag_g AS fib2mag_g, po.extinction_g AS extinct_g,  	po.modelmag_r AS modmag_r, po.modelmagerr_r AS moderr_r, po.fibermag_r AS fib3mag_r, po.fiber2mag_r AS fib2mag_r, po.extinction_r AS extinct_r,  	po.modelmag_i AS modmag_i, po.modelmagerr_i AS moderr_i, po.fibermag_i AS fib3mag_i, po.fiber2mag_i AS fib2mag_i, po.extinction_i AS extinct_i,  	po.modelmag_z AS modmag_z, po.modelmagerr_z AS moderr_z, po.fibermag_z AS fib3mag_z, po.fiber2mag_z AS fib2mag_z, po.extinction_z AS extinct_z, 	ISNULL(mp.ptsKey, #) AS tmass_ptskey, ISNULL(mp.ra, #) AS tmass_ra, ISNULL(mp.dec, #) AS tmass_dec,  	ISNULL(mp.errMaj, #) AS tmass_errmaj, ISNULL(mp.errMin, #) AS tmass_errmin,  	ISNULL(mp.j, #) AS tmass_mag_j, ISNULL(mp.jIvar, #) AS tmass_ivar_j, ISNULL(mp.nDetectJ, #) AS tmass_ndet_j,  	ISNULL(mp.h, #) AS tmass_mag_h, ISNULL(mp.hIvar, #) AS tmass_ivar_h, ISNULL(mp.nDetectH, #) AS tmass_ndet_h,  	ISNULL(mp.k, #) AS tmass_mag_k, ISNULL(mp.kIvar, #) AS tmass_ivar_k, ISNULL(mp.nDetectK, #) AS tmass_ndet_k,  	ISNULL(mp.phqual, #) AS tmass_quality,  	ISNULL(mp.ccFlag, #) AS tmass_ccflag,  	ISNULL(mp.galContam, #) AS tmass_galcont,  	ISNULL(mx.ext_key, #) AS tmass_extkey,  	ISNULL(mx.j_m_k2#fe, #) AS tmxsc_mag_j, ISNULL(mx.j_msig_k2#fe, #) AS tmxsc_sig_j, 	ISNULL(mx.h_m_k2#fe, #) AS tmxsc_mag_h, ISNULL(mx.h_msig_k2#fe, #) AS tmxsc_sig_h, 	ISNULL(mx.k_m_k2#fe, #) AS tmxsc_mag_k, ISNULL(mx.k_msig_k2#fe, #) AS tmxsc_sig_k  INTO MyDB.XMC_full_SDSS_data FROM MyDB.XMC_full_SDSS_objid tmp 	     INNER JOIN PhotoPrimary po ON po.objid      = tmp.objid 	LEFT OUTER JOIN Photoz       pz ON pz.objid      = po.objid 	LEFT OUTER JOIN SpecObj      sp ON sp.bestobjid  = po.objid 	LEFT OUTER JOIN PlateX       pl ON pl.plateid    = sp.plateid 	LEFT OUTER JOIN TwoMass      mp ON mp.objid      = po.objid 	LEFT OUTER JOIN TwoMassXSC   mx ON mx.objid      = po.objid ORDER BY phot_id
